The economic imperatives for technology enabled wellness centered healthcare.

Jones GB(1)(2), Wright JM(3).

Author information:
(1)Connected Health Program, Global Drug Development, Novartis Pharmaceuticals, 
1 Health Plaza, East Hanover, NJ, 07936, USA. graham.jones@novartis.com.
(2)Clinical and Translational Science Institute, Tufts University Medical 
