Atezolizumab with chemotherapy in first-line treatment for metastatic urothelial 
cancer: a cost-effectiveness analysis.

Zhang PF(1)(2)(3)(4), Wen F(1)(2), Wu QJ(1)(2), Li Q(1)(2).

